Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.48,0:02:10.70,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fun Fun 梦想　Shout Shout 传达
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.81,0:02:14.04,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失误的话就当排练再来一回！
