Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.50,0:00:04.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.17,0:00:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还得把日记交给老师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.91,0:00:08.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.21,0:00:11.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  今天是值日吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.08,0:00:14.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  本来应该是小唯的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.21,0:00:19.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…从午休开始一直处于那种状态
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.97,0:00:22.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我叫过她好几次了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.98,0:00:26.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  唯  起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.07,0:00:29.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  唯  快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.83,0:00:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  忧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.05,0:00:33.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是周日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.83,0:00:36.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多么积极的想法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.24,0:00:41.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  唯  要练习啦  要开演唱会啦  要弹吉他啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.80,0:00:46.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  要吃蛋糕啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.80,0:00:46.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯  要吃蛋糕啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.21,0:00:57.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有  你们骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.18,0:00:58.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.32,0:01:02.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不行    把真蛋糕拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.39,0:01:03.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.74,0:01:04.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田井中同学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.67,0:01:07.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.10,0:01:09.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.30,0:01:14.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前借给你们的布偶装差不多该还了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.44,0:01:16.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演剧部好像要用
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.66,0:01:17.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布偶装？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.28,0:01:20.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律  你还没还吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.10,0:01:22.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那个的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.77,0:01:26.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前段时间为了招揽新人穿过后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.49,0:01:28.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就放到储物室里了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.32,0:01:29.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是还回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.55,0:01:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.82,0:01:34.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.53,0:01:38.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想  布偶装的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.43,0:01:40.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.14,0:01:44.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.31,0:01:51.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻音猪…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.33,0:03:29.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我们来大扫除
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.07,0:03:32.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个  别露出这么一副明显不想干的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.95,0:03:36.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  今天加油来练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.34,0:03:37.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得没错  小律
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.60,0:03:39.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标是武道馆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.62,0:03:41.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么不想干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.02,0:03:43.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:46.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比第三顿饭更讨厌大扫除！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:46.44,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（出自江戸時代的「三度の飯より喧嘩が好き」，那时一天只有两顿饭，\N实际应该是「比第三顿饭更喜欢〇〇」的形式）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.55,0:03:47.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.28,0:03:49.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说了  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.72,0:03:54.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的扫除由音乐教室的卫生值日生来做不就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:55.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.82,0:03:57.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来是应该那样…
