Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:06.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是满是私人物品  而是只有私人物品
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:08.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说得没错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.46,0:04:11.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～我的呱呱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.28,0:04:12.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就来收拾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.08,0:04:14.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明之前放得好好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.49,0:04:15.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了不要放回去！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.03,0:04:19.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没办法  就认真地来干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.62,0:04:21.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这量还真多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.88,0:04:26.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么私人物品的话  都暂且把这里当作仓库堆着了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.69,0:04:29.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这成堆的布偶是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.22,0:04:33.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那个大的只用了二百日元就入手了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.51,0:04:34.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又没问你那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:36.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快  拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:39.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.99,0:04:41.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  这个也一起拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.41,0:04:43.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  这个不是我的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:44.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？那…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.29,0:04:49.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是澪的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.13,0:04:52.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然把咖啡套具也带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.59,0:04:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但结果都没用过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.83,0:04:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  餐具橱也要扫除吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.60,0:04:59.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  难得扫除一次  就顺便一起收拾了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.31,0:05:03.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新来看一下的话  好像真的很昂贵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.27,0:05:06.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些餐具要多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.85,0:05:09.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…价格我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.00,0:05:12.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但听说和比利时王室用的是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.23,0:05:14.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王室？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.65,0:05:16.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.55,0:05:20.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大部分都收拾好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.91,0:05:22.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.02,0:05:25.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我们的私人物品也有很多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.43,0:05:29.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是以前轻音部的私人物品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.29,0:05:32.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前好像有很多部员呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:35.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也曾经认真干过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.54,0:05:37.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.42,0:05:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.41,0:05:44.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈  好像很贵重的箱子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.71,0:05:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有装什么值钱的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.09,0:05:49.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:54.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很旧  但好像很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.80,0:05:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还期待会出现更有趣的东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.24,0:05:58.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.57,0:06:01.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是轻音部  应该感兴趣才对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:03.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  好怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:04.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.72,0:06:06.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.37,0:06:09.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  这是老师的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.67,0:06:12.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然都没怎么用过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:15.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师以前是轻音部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.96,0:06:17.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  我没说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:20.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  果然是那样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:24.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学园祭的时候演奏得非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.64,0:06:25.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:29.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有段空白期  但比现在的小唯要弹得好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.11,0:06:31.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次教教我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.77,0:06:32.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.06,0:06:37.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便说一下  这个就是学生时期的小佐和
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.73,0:06:38.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.80,0:06:39.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私人物品大家都会各自拿回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以小佐和也拿回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.28,0:06:46.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.11,0:06:50.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好浓的霉味
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:53.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过也没时间来弹了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.76,0:06:55.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  那这个吉他怎么处理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.53,0:07:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它卖到店里去  来增加部费吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.74,0:07:02.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真大方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.42,0:07:03.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.32,0:07:04.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个塞给我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.97,0:07:08.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  这个不是好东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.64,0:07:11.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是从我爸爸的朋友那里得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:16.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种保存状态的话  已经不行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.22,0:07:19.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  如果能卖掉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.95,0:07:23.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让别人去用  对它来说也是一种幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.35,0:07:27.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜～好浓的霉味～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.49,0:07:30.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分～尽让我来拿～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.60,0:07:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜拳三连败是你自己不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.91,0:07:35.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.11,0:07:38.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的包也很重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.57,0:07:41.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是你自己的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.50,0:07:44.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:45.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.57,0:07:46.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.42,0:07:48.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.06,0:07:50.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定不会输
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.82,0:07:52.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.93,0:07:55.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我把你打回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.61,0:08:00.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像小孩子一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:01.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.45,0:08:03.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.35,0:08:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  看见了  这是剪刀？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.33,0:08:08.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,  不能说出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:11.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  澪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.58,0:08:12.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来猜拳啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.79,0:08:13.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.50,0:08:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才拿的传单？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.57,0:08:18.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些东西能放在准备室里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.22,0:08:19.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橱柜？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.34,0:08:22.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一个就能把很多东西整理进去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.13,0:08:24.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.36,0:08:27.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个价格的话  用部费也能买
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.08,0:08:33.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看  家具卖场在…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:35.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是Home Center？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.26,0:08:37.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.93,0:08:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多方便的商品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.44,0:08:44.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小不同的电灯泡之类的  七色的塑料胶带之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.78,0:08:45.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…有是有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.63,0:08:48.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,  你是第一次来Home Center吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:49.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.57,0:08:52.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都想要来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.09,0:08:55.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.46,0:08:57.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.44,0:09:00.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  唯  吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.11,0:09:04.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀哎呀哎呀  好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.46,0:09:09.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  这是能很漂亮地修补墙破洞的笔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.12,0:09:10.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.25,0:09:14.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是能轻松整理旧杂志的纸胶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.73,0:09:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么稀奇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.62,0:09:17.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.33,0:09:20.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个擦水龙头就会变得闪亮闪亮？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.38,0:09:23.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.90,0:09:27.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐  还有这种东西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:31.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能把蛋糕精确地八等分的切蛋糕刀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.28,0:09:33.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像伞一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.60,0:09:35.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能用这个切吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.77,0:09:36.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来下  来下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.80,0:09:38.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看  快看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.02,0:09:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多螺丝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯学姐也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:43.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些全都是螺丝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.03,0:09:46.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.40,0:09:47.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看  快看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.57,0:09:48.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好酷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.77,0:09:53.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.33,0:09:55.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电动拧螺丝枪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.14,0:09:57.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砰  砰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.47,0:09:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  真吵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:00.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  你们两个死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.58,0:10:01.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不不…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:03.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.51,0:10:04.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:06.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯真是小孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:08.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.57,0:10:09.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好刺眼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.08,0:10:11.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快摘掉  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.21,0:10:13.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.54,0:10:14.18,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.28,0:10:16.59,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要随便乱弄店里的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.69,0:10:18.90,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  好痛好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.26,0:10:18.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵  梓喵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.03,0:10:20.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次又是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.61,0:10:22.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿这个动起来很方便哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.59,0:10:23.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太松了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.18,0:10:25.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为演唱会时穿的衣服怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.26,0:10:28.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在背后写上「放学后茶会」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.25,0:10:30.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴走族吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.70,0:10:33.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.04,0:10:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐和子老师说可以放在活动室里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.84,0:10:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那让他们明天放学后送到学校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.63,0:10:42.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯她们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.77,0:10:44.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这附近吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.55,0:10:46.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.37,0:10:48.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:51.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你买了多少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.21,0:11:00.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌龟？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.05,0:11:01.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳖？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.69,0:11:03.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:04.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.94,0:11:06.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.17,0:11:07.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种地方请不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.63,0:11:10.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.78,0:11:13.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  好可爱的鳖啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.50,0:11:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:17.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是鳖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.51,0:11:21.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在鳖之中也是脱颖而出的美人啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.21,0:11:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…这是猪鼻龟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.21,0:11:25.29,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（猪鼻龟（Pig-Nosed Turtle），又称飞河龟（Fly River Turtle），\N学名Carettochelys insculpta）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:27.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是乌龟  乌龟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.39,0:11:30.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可爱得想把花生放进它鼻子里～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.61,0:11:32.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算是什么可爱的程度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.66,0:11:39.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到从那里开始会是四连败
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:40.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜利的剪刀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.65,0:11:42.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就让我来核定一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.09,0:11:43.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.48,0:11:49.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在看什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:55.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的乐队要是有这么多人的话  会演奏出怎样的音乐来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:11:59.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  要是有这么多部员就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.01,0:12:04.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待核定的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:07.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.07,0:12:12.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个吉他  我们用五十万日元买下了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.28,0:12:16.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五十万日元？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.31,0:12:20.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K-ON!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.69,0:12:24.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.57,0:12:26.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.94,0:12:28.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.99,0:12:29.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.57,0:12:33.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是…五五五…五百万…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.80,0:12:35.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淡定点  价位都变了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.86,0:12:37.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.22,0:12:38.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也太淡定了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.14,0:12:42.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会是这个价啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是在照顾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.75,0:12:47.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  和那个没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.79,0:12:52.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这把吉他的原型为1960年代最初的吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.26,0:12:55.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当初材料和造型都没有固定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.03,0:12:58.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经过各种局部改造之后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:01.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才成为现在的模样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.52,0:13:04.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位带来的这把吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.92,0:13:06.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指板是一种叫做蓝花楹的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.92,0:13:06.77,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（指板(fingerboard)：特指除拇指以外四个手指接触部分的木材）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.08,0:13:09.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现今非常贵重的木材制成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.25,0:13:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是出高价的原因之一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:17.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗憾的是  这把吉他的系弦板被更换过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.26,0:13:21.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是完全原装  所以价格稍微下降了些
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.31,0:13:25.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但停条系弦板更有演奏性
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.31,0:13:25.01,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（停条系弦板(Stop Tailpiece)：六孔穿弦金属条式，属于最常见的类型，延音效果不错）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.37,0:13:27.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多顾客更偏爱这种
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.80,0:13:29.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以也算不上太大的缺点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.32,0:13:33.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且这把吉他被长期封存
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.10,0:13:36.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有过多损伤琴身和琴格
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.10,0:13:36.09,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（琴格(fret)：镶嵌于指板的薄金属细条，用于改变弦的音高）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.44,0:13:39.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为年代物来说条件非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.39,0:13:41.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就以这个价格收购了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.49,0:13:46.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总…总之是很贵重的吉他！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.85,0:13:48.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厚！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.67,0:13:52.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是巨无霸嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.32,0:13:53.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没讲汉堡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.15,0:13:57.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说薯条是不是太多了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:13:59.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这么多钱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.50,0:14:01.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薯条XL Size
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.51,0:14:02.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用找了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.40,0:14:04.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你花了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:06.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没  这个是自掏腰包
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.07,0:14:10.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  这样好吗  大家分？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:14.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法吧  小佐和都说用作部费了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:15.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼唧哼唧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.87,0:14:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.78,0:14:19.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧！五个人平分一人十万！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.78,0:14:26.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有个效果器挺想要来着…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.26,0:14:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:28.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵陷落
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.79,0:14:31.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！别把那么多钱拿出来炫耀！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:34.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看～澪也有十万哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:37.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十万啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.19,0:14:39.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有十万…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.08,0:14:44.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要多重贝司音箱模拟和新的放大器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.42,0:14:48.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想要双踏板和落地鼓啦 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.73,0:14:50.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等钱上脸的感觉如何啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.21,0:14:52.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～继续～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.56,0:14:58.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…各位？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:15:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里这里～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.22,0:15:04.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.06,0:15:06.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收拾得很干净呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.00,0:15:07.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.85,0:15:09.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.91,0:15:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.65,0:15:16.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说好了私人物品拿回家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.71,0:15:20.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  除了昨天带回去的还剩下这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.95,0:15:23.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是再往回搬  一定会惹忧生气的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:26.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是放在这里  生气的人就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.98,0:15:29.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忧才吓人呢  昨天她还那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:31.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.69,0:15:34.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶了我吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.94,0:15:37.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全都没有姐姐的威严啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.38,0:15:39.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了  过后我一定收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.03,0:15:41.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先在这里放一阵子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:44.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊  只能放这些哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.19,0:15:46.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.64,0:15:48.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.27,0:15:49.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀呵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:52.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橱柜送来啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.33,0:15:55.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  感觉不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.49,0:15:56.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.33,0:16:02.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？人家和你们说话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.51,0:16:05.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.47,0:16:10.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和～怎么你来啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.71,0:16:12.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家都没听到～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.48,0:16:14.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是  昨天怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.65,0:16:15.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  昨天？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.00,0:16:18.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的吉他啊  卖了多少钱？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:22.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那个啊…卖了多少来着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.91,0:16:24.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得…好像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.90,0:16:28.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因…因为挺老的  好像50年前的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:30.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.27,0:16:34.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀？那么说小佐和其实已经是50岁的人啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.37,0:16:38.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪里见过这么精神的50岁！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:39.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.47,0:16:41.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.78,0:16:44.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说过是我爸爸的朋友送的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.88,0:16:46.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来的确…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.56,0:16:49.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是  到底卖了多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.42,0:16:51.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这  这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.31,0:16:54.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一…一万元
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.84,0:16:56.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也太贪了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.56,0:17:01.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉…顺口就…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:02.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然也就那么点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.21,0:17:04.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都发霉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:08.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把发票给我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.30,0:17:10.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:13.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要算进部费里的  当然需要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.15,0:17:17.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难道没要？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.78,0:17:19.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.48,0:17:21.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.81,0:17:31.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉啦～勇者啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.60,0:17:35.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快吃！快吃！快吃！快吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.64,0:17:38.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么！快吐出来！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.17,0:17:38.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没门！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.50,0:17:40.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给老娘吐出来！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.84,0:17:42.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.89,0:17:43.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呕…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.80,0:17:48.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧！卖了五十万？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:49.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也太厉害了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.37,0:17:52.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是非常贵重的东西！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.57,0:17:55.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还请恕罪！小的本无意隐瞒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.92,0:17:59.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但金额庞大  小的一时动了邪念…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.19,0:18:01.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太肮脏了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.88,0:18:03.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她从前就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.50,0:18:05.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们有什么资格说我！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.61,0:18:10.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  那就把小律说的一万元当作部费好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.06,0:18:13.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便顶上橱柜钱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.45,0:18:15.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～就那么点？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.37,0:18:18.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是一开始就讲实话的话  我还打算全给你们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.38,0:18:21.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你绝对在骗人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.63,0:18:25.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是律不好  不知道你想藏什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.72,0:18:30.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊  我本来就觉得直接说出来比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.26,0:18:31.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然还有脸说！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.36,0:18:32.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.67,0:18:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:34.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后我还有一个愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:36.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用那沓钱来抽…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.43,0:18:39.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抽我的脸吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.82,0:18:43.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太幸福了～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.72,0:18:46.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是你好啊…真和谐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.36,0:18:48.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.13,0:18:52.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再特别让你们用这笔钱买一件东西好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.12,0:18:54.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.48,0:18:57.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想买什么  大家商量好再说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.87,0:18:59.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一件啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.79,0:19:02.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说一个啦  我要来五个！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.77,0:19:04.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要脸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:04.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.43,0:19:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.01,0:19:10.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,添个放大器最合适了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.26,0:19:15.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是觉得效果器比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.62,0:19:18.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪样都不是大家都能用的东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.08,0:19:19.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提议！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:20.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:22.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多买一只呱呱如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.98,0:19:25.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一对的话  绝对会有新部员加入的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.98,0:19:26.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.79,0:19:27.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎呱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.35,0:19:31.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,球拍不要握得太紧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.76,0:19:34.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用全身的力量去打球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.04,0:19:37.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光用手劲的话  手腕和手肘会痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.70,0:19:38.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.48,0:19:39.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.89,0:19:43.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管哪个社团都有新部员加入并正式开始活动了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.34,0:19:44.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.41,0:19:46.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.83,0:19:51.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.24,0:19:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…虽然说「五个人就好了」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.24,0:19:57.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但终究是想要个学妹的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.17,0:20:00.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也这么觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.85,0:20:02.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.38,0:20:07.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵来的时候  我们都很高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.08,0:20:09.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法  那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.48,0:20:16.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪位新同学…请带我去音乐室…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.53,0:20:17.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个已经试过了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.98,0:20:19.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.76,0:20:25.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想到个好主意！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.81,0:20:35.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.60,0:20:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是新成员小猪～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.99,0:20:42.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托老师买回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.28,0:20:44.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓的学妹哦  多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.98,0:20:53.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  不觉得反应太淡了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.98,0:20:54.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.88,0:20:55.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.63,0:20:59.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说梓喜欢这乌龟的可是唯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.05,0:21:03.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时梓喵明明一副很想要的样子盯着看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.60,0:21:05.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盯着看的是唯学姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.32,0:21:09.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是觉得那张脸好怪而看看而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.98,0:21:10.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.56,0:21:12.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞砸了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.27,0:21:15.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.85,0:21:18.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但为什么突然这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.59,0:21:20.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.66,0:21:24.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们觉得小梓没有学妹是不是寂寞了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.55,0:21:25.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.24,0:21:28.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄来了新人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.26,0:21:41.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  被这么随便的人买来养  太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.89,0:21:45.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点头了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.53,0:21:47.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.19,0:21:52.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  今后我来好好照顾你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.61,0:21:55.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不  我也会好好照顾的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.90,0:21:57.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯学姐做不来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.04,0:22:00.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.13,0:23:45.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.86,0:23:46.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.09,0:23:48.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从成为班主任后
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.91,0:23:51.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和变得皮肤滑滑～头发亮亮～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.06,0:23:54.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家不觉得她异常充实吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.04,0:23:56.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想闪闪发光！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.86,0:24:00.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  它在看小唯了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.42,0:24:01.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼仪很不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.16,0:24:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正像这样在黑暗中思考着闪闪发光小律大作战
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.95,0:24:09.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？


